Modifications by SideYomi:

- JMdict English glosses were machine-translated into Korean (Anthropic Claude, Haiku).
- Tatoeba Japanese example sentences were machine-translated into Korean (Anthropic Claude, Haiku).

Per the EDRDG licence, JMdict data should be kept reasonably current; regenerate
this bundle periodically from the latest JMdict release (see scripts/build-dict/README.md).

